## Performance Analysis — `Truncation.cs`

**Context:** Hot path — every displayed string, thousands of concurrent users.

### Scan Execution Checklist

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| IndexOf/Substring without StringComparison | 0 |
| Sync-over-async | 0 |
| `.Split(` | 1 |
| `.TrimEnd()` (allocating) | 1 |
| `string +` concat (allocating) | 3 |
